- Benar.

462
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:26,009
Ranjang, meja, dan sandaran lengan di sofa.

463
00:27:26,009 --> 00:27:29,019
Kita harus memindai semuanya.

464
00:27:34,150 --> 00:27:35,160
Bukan begitu?

465
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,539
"Lee Hye Seong"

466
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:54,539
Lihatlah di sini.

467
00:28:05,289 --> 00:28:07,690
Mari selesaikan nanti. Aku ada tamu.

468
00:28:17,630 --> 00:28:19,869
